    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://chicago.craigslist.org/chc/ret/6039401175.html"></div>
        </div>
The Bakery Team Member is responsible for providing exceptional guest service. They will make sure the Bakery section of the store is well stocked for our guests.  They assist in receiving, storing and stocking of products while ensuring proper rotation and quality.  They will build displays, handle damaged product and maintain a proper fronting of the department. <br>
<br>
Qualifications:<br>
<br>
·          Ability to provide exceptional guest service.<br>
<br>
·          Knowledgeable and Passionate about Bakery products.<br>
<br>
·          Excellent written and verbal communication skills.<br>
<br>
·          Must be Self-motivated and able to work independently.<br>
<br>
·          Must be detail oriented and able to work quickly and efficiently at the same time.<br>
<br>
·          Ability to work a variety of shifts including nights, weekends and holidays.<br>
<br>
·          Able to stand and walk for up to 4 hours without a break<br>
<br>
·          Able to bend and stoop to grasp objects, climb ladders, lift loads up to 50 lbs. unassisted, push and pull carts up to 100lbs. unassisted.<br>
<br>
Responsibilities: <br>
<br>
·          Responsible for achieving 90% or higher average on all Mystery shop scores.<br>
<br>
·          Effectively resolve guest issues.<br>
<br>
·          Follow proper rotation guidelines.<br>
<br>
·          Adhere to Plum Market expectations for proper fronting of the department.<br>
<br>
·          Maintain proper signage and pricing.<br>
<br>
·          Follow all backstock and  topstock procedures.<br>
<br>
·          Maintain a clean and organized back room.<br>
<br>
·          Effectively communicate with Guests, Team Members and Store Leadership.<br>
<br>
·          Thorough knowledge of all relevant Plum Market policies and standards.<br>
<br>
  Benefits<br>
<br>
  Medical and Dental Plans<br>
  Paid Vacations<br>
  401k Option<br>
  20% Team Member Discount<br>
  50% Shift Meal Discount<br>
<br>
  Employment is contingent on a successful background check,<br>
<br>
  Apply online at www.plummarket.com/careers.    </section>

